For example, if a patience presents 3 myocardial conditions a value of 3 will be assign to its myocardial summary variable.

for (col in names(my_data)) {
  max <- max(my_data[[col]])
  hist(my_data[[col]], main = paste("Histogram of", col), xlab = col, labels = TRUE, breaks=max)
  #hist(data_lived[[col]], main = paste("Histogram of", col), xlab = col, labels = TRUE)
  #hist(data_died[[col]], main = paste("Histogram of", col), xlab = col, labels = TRUE)
  med = mean(my_data[[col]])
  abline(v = med, col = 'blue')
  mdn = median(my_data[[col]])
  abline(v = mdn, col = 'red')
}
